      &lt;h1 class=&quot;mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-amber-400 sm:text-5xl&quot; id=&quot;desde-experimentos-en-matraces-hasta-ensayos-industriales&quot;&gt;
